# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:30
translate spanish hwb_s10a_d63cf465:

    # "I wake up slowly, fighting to keep my eyes open. In the back of my head, I feel like something is wrong."
    "Me despierto lentamente, luchando por mantener los ojos abiertos. En el fondo de mi cabeza, siento que algo está mal."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:32
translate spanish hwb_s10a_9d42a60d:

    # "It takes a minute before I realize I’ve overslept."
    "Tardo un minuto en darme cuenta de que he dormido de más."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:34
translate spanish hwb_s10a_46a8ac3e:

    # "It’s a quarter to six. Marina was supposed to wake me up 15 minutes ago."
    "Son un cuarto para las seis. Marina debió despertarme hace 15 minutos."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s10a_0c333ccf:

    # Amber "Marina?"
    Amber "Марина?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s10a_ac09de71:

    # "I call her name, but get no response."
    "La llamo por su nombre, pero no obtengo respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:42
translate spanish hwb_s10a_ac99ed12:

    # "Rolling out of bed, I massage my eyes and stumble up towards the front."
    "Rodando fuera de la cama, me masajeo los ojos y tropiezo hacia el frente."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s10a_43bb14e4:

    # "Of course she’s asleep. Sprawled out on the dash, with her head buried in her arms. It looks like she’s been out for a while."
    "Por supuesto que está dormida. Tirada sobre el tablero, con la cabeza enterrada entre sus brazos. Parece que lleva un rato así."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s10a_185c79d1:

    # "Jerking her by the shoulder, I shake her awake."
    "Agarrándola del hombro, la sacudo para despertarla."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s10a_dcf37c4f:

    # Marina "{cps=80}Wha-{w=0.8}what’s up, Amber?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=80}Что-{w=0.8}Что случилось, Эмбер?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s10a_59ee71ac:

    # "Her speech is slurred by sleepiness."
    "Su habla está arrastrada por el sueño."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s10a_500f5adc:

    # "I ignore the temptation to make the \"not you\" joke."
    "Ignoro la tentación de hacer el chiste de \"tú no\"."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s10a_086dfc45:

    # Amber "How’s that book you’re reading?"
    Amber "Как тебе книга?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s10a_7d52af64:

    # Marina "It’s great! I just put it down to-"
    Marina "Замечательно! Я только отложила ее, чтобы-"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s10a_3c742783:

    # "A look of shock spreads across her face."
    "Una expresión de shock se extiende por su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s10a_da00b9c1:

    # "Mounting horror takes over as she realizes the time."
    "Un horror creciente la invade al darse cuenta de la hora."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s10a_71af970c:

    # Marina "Oh God, I’m so, so sorry. I was just gonna nap but then I forgot. To set an alarm I mean. To wake me up."
    Marina "О Боже, мне так, так жаль. Я собиралась только вздремнуть и забылась. В смысле забыла поставить будильник. Чтобы он разбудил меня."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c2829ab8:

    # Amber "Yeah, that’s what alarms are for."
    Amber "Ага, для этого будильники и существуют."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s10a_ad634dde:

    # "Freaking out, she hurriedly tries to buckle her seatbelt, failing several times in her frenzy."
    "Enloquecida, intenta apresuradamente abrocharse el cinturón de seguridad, fallando varias veces en su frenesí."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s10a_7ad5395d:

    # "I pat her on the shoulder as I sit down. It's not even a big deal, but she's so worked up."
    "Le doy una palmada en el hombro mientras me siento. Ni siquiera es gran cosa, pero ella está tan alterada."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s10a_92f77012:

    # Amber "It’s cool. We’re not late yet. Ready to go?"
    Amber "Охладись. Мы не опаздываем. Ты готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s10a_0804ce2f:

    # "Marina just nods, staring at the floor."
    "Marina solo asiente, mirando al suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s10a_709cccb2:

    # "I buckle up and turn the key. The engine roars to life, and I throw it in reverse. I have to crane my neck to make sure I don’t run over anyone."
    "Me abrocho el cinturón y giro la llave. El motor ruge a la vida, y lo pongo en reversa. Tengo que estirar el cuello para asegurarme de no atropellar a nadie."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s10a_4bc17061:

    # "Road-signs direct us out of town and towards the canyon. After spending so long on the highway, going down these streets with lower speed limits feels restrictive."
    "Las señales de tránsito nos sacan del pueblo y nos dirigen hacia el cañón. Después de pasar tanto tiempo en la carretera, bajar por estas calles con límites de velocidad más bajos se siente restrictivo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s10a_0e43fe4c:

    # "From the corner of my eye, I watch Marina. She’s being abnormally quiet."
    "De reojo, observo a Marina. Está anormalmente callada."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s10a_5ad1b6b5:

    # "She fixes her hair, pops her knuckles, and rubs her shoulders, but she doesn’t say anything."
    "Se arregla el cabello, se cruje los nudillos y se frota los hombros, pero no dice nada."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s10a_e10647c8:

    # "Finally, I cave."
    "Finalmente, cedo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s10a_f230f7cd:

    # Amber "What’s wrong with you?"
    Amber "Что с тобой такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s10a_67ab0d58:

    # Marina "Huh? What do you mean?"
    Marina "А? Что ты имеешь в виду?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s10a_5f9ac29b:

    # "Her tone of voice is stressed. Maybe I’m more intimidating than I think."
    "Su tono de voz es tenso. Quizás soy más intimidante de lo que creo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s10a_778c659a:

    # Amber "You’re being weird. Super quiet."
    Amber "Ты ведешь себя странно. Слишком тихо."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s10a_57f44337:

    # Marina "Oh. Um."
    Marina "Ой. Эм."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s10a_5738f5c2:

    # Amber "Um?"
    Amber "Эм?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s10a_b8271406:

    # Marina "I didn’t know if you were mad at me or not."
    Marina "Я не знала, рассердилась ты на меня или нет."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s10a_7885ccfd:

    # Amber "What, for falling asleep?"
    Amber "За что? За то, что ты уснула?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s10a_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s10a_19bedb77:

    # Amber "Pfft."
    Amber "Пффф."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s10a_8f010861:

    # Amber "Nah, I’m not mad. Trust me, you’d know for sure if I was."
    Amber "Неа, я не сержусь. Поверь мне, ты бы точно поняла, если бы я рассердилась."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s10a_aa3a10a0:

    # Amber "I told you it wasn't a big deal, didn't I?"
    Amber "Я же сказала тебе, что ничего страшного, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s10a_fcbb6cf0:

    # Marina "You promise?"
    Marina "Честно?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s10a_88109dfa:

    # Amber "Yeah, I promise."
    Amber "Ага, честно."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s10a_502048a2:

    # "Marina bounces in her seat, immediately cheerier."
    "Marina brinca en su asiento, de inmediato más alegre."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s10a_366e59a0:

    # Marina "Okay cool. ‘Cause like, if you were mad at me already that’d be a bad sign."
    Marina "Отлично, круто. Потому что, если бы ты на меня уже сейчас разозлилась, то это был бы плохой знак."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s10a_acf05a7a:

    # Amber "Sign of what?"
    Amber "Знак чего?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c305a2af:

    # Marina "That we wouldn’t be good partners! You know, treasure hunting buddies?"
    Marina "Что мы не сработаемся как напарники! Ну, знаешь, не станем приятелями по поиску сокровищ."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s10a_1e6c464b:

    # Amber "Oh, we’re partners now, are we? You’re the sidekick, right?"
    Amber "О, так мы уже напарники? И ты что-то вроде ассистента, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s10a_09fd6307:

    # Marina "No way! I’m totally the main character. We’re here because of me."
    Marina "Еще чего! Я самый что ни на есть главарь. Мы здесь именно благодаря мне."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s10a_fa5df7a7:

    # "I laugh, and she turns away smiling. She’s a lot cuter when she smiles."
    "Me río, y ella voltea sonriendo. Es mucho más linda cuando sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s10a_62edb19b:

    # "I’ve been smiling more, too, I realize. As I think that, it starts to make me sad again."
    "Me he estado riendo más seguido también, me doy cuenta. Al pensar eso, vuelve a entristecerme."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s10a_b77c40f3:

    # "Do I really deserve to be smiling right now?"
    "¿Acaso merezco estar sonriendo ahora mismo?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s10a_93cd1da8:

    # Marina "Hey Amber?"
    Marina "Эй, Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s10a_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Да?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s10a_0d56cd81:

    # "Like she read my mind, Marina snaps me out of it."
    "Como si me hubiera leído la mente, Marina me saca de ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s10a_6a11b5f0:

    # Marina "Can we listen to Super Crush again?"
    Marina "Может снова включим «Super Crush»?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s10a_daa11d7d:

    # Amber "You seriously liked that one?"
    Amber "Тебе правда они понравились?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s10a_285bd9a0:

    # "Super Crush was one of those groups that Gramps loved to show off to other people, because they were so weird. All of the members played a different instrument on each album, so it was like a whole other band every time."
    "Super Crush era uno de esos grupos que al Abuelo le encantaba presumirle a los demás, porque eran muy raros. Todos los miembros tocaban un instrumento diferente en cada álbum, así que era como una banda completamente distinta cada vez."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s10a_7dc05ece:

    # Marina "{cps=80}Yeah!{w=0.5} It was{cps=2}... {cps=80}Different.{w=0.7} But in a good way.{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=80}Ага!{w=0.5} Их музыка была{cps=2}... {cps=80}Другой.{w=0.7} Но в хорошем смысле.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s10a_1c51c809:

    # Amber "That’s definitely true."
    Amber "Совершенно верно."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s10a_61e80dc7:

    # "With one hand on the steering wheel, I dig around in the bin of tapes by my feet. I flick my gaze between that and the road. Eventually I find the one I’m looking for - it has a Halloween-orange case with text that looks like slime."
    "Con una mano en el volante, busco en el bote de casetes junto a mis pies. Muevo la mirada entre eso y la carretera. Finalmente encuentro el que busco: tiene una funda naranja Halloween con texto que parece baba."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s10a_f9315950:

    # "When it starts to play, Marina hums along. She’s almost on-key. Guess she liked it enough to remember how the songs go."
    "Cuando empieza a sonar, Marina tararea. Casi está en tono. Supongo que le gustó lo suficiente como para recordar cómo van las canciones."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s10a_993f4a67:

    # "I crank the volume up, earning a grin from Marina. The sound is tinny and distorted at this level. More distorted than usual, I mean. But it’s also more fun."
    "Subo el volumen, ganándome una sonrisa de Marina. El sonido es metálico y distorsionado a este nivel. Más distorsionado de lo normal, quiero decir. Pero también es más divertido."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s10a_90689df9:

    # "Our smiles last all the way until we roll into a nearly-empty parking lot."
    "Nuestras sonrisas duran hasta que llegamos a un estacionamiento casi vacío."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s10a_8bf03b57:

    # "As I turn the volume back down, I can tell she's thinking the same thing I am."
    "Mientras bajo el volumen de nuevo, puedo notar que está pensando lo mismo que yo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s10a_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s10a_343b94ea:

    # Amber "Yeah?"
    Amber "Да?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a3b3c7d6:

    # Marina "{cps=80}Shouldn’t there be like{cps=4}…{w=0.4} {cps=80}Other people waiting here?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=80}Разве тут не должны быть{cps=4}…{w=0.4} {cps=80}и другие люди?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s10a_f56ee0f5:

    # Amber "There probably should. What time is it?"
    Amber "Вообще-то должны. Который час?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s10a_e6ddc6b3:

    # "Marina twists around to check."
    "Marina se gira para revisar."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c7e63220:

    # Marina "Uh, 6:20."
    Marina "Э-э, 6:20."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s10a_af376d4d:

    # Amber "What the hell, did they start early?"
    Amber "Какого черта, они что, ушли раньше?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s10a_bd6733e4:

    # "There are other cars around, but they’re all unoccupied. My parking job is hasty and I take up two spaces, but don’t bother to correct it."
    "Hay otros autos alrededor, pero todos están desocupados. Mi estacionamiento es apresurado y ocupo dos espacios, pero no me molesto en corregirlo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s10a_fc6fdfdd:

    # "We hurry out of the RV. I almost forget the key in the ignition and have to double back to grab it. Marina’s already over at an information desk, probably talking to a ranger."
    "Salimos corriendo de la casa rodante. Casi olvido la llave en el encendido y tengo que regresar por ella. Marina ya está en un mostrador de información, probablemente hablando con un guardabosques."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s10a_bcd1ae15:

    # "But then she turns back to me, the despair on her face visible even though it’s getting dark."
    "Pero entonces se vuelve hacia mí, la desesperación en su rostro visible aunque ya está oscureciendo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s10a_1975d98c:

    # Marina "There’s no one here!"
    Marina "Тут никого нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s10a_eb6ef47f:

    # "There aren’t any lights on inside, either. Probably closed at six. I vaguely recall reading that in a brochure, but I thought there would still be someone around for the tours."
    "Tampoco hay luces encendidas adentro. Probablemente cerraron a las seis. Recuerdo vagamente haber leído eso en un folleto, pero pensé que aún habría alguien para los recorridos."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a572b79f:

    # Amber "Don’t panic!"
    Amber "Без паники!"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s10a_d30eb909:

    # "I jog back to the RV and unlock it again. Rummaging through the glovebox, I pull out the little blue flashlight that Gramps gave me a few years ago."
    "Vuelvo corriendo a la casa rodante y la desbloqueo de nuevo. Revolviendo la guantera, saco la pequeña linterna azul que el Abuelo me dio hace unos años."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s10a_52e5545f:

    # "I click it on and off a couple times to make sure that it works."
    "La enciendo y apago un par de veces para asegurarme de que funcione."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c4b63248:

    # "After I lock everything back up again, I join Marina by the unhelpful help desk. She’s bouncing on her heels, hands clasped together."
    "Después de volver a cerrar todo, me uno a Marina junto al mostrador de ayuda inútil. Está rebotando sobre sus talones, con las manos juntas."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a78d91cf:

    # Amber "Hey, it’s alright. Worse comes to worst we’ll just do it tomorrow."
    Amber "Эй, все нормально. На крайний случай мы провернем все завтра."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a24000e3:

    # Marina "But what if someone else finds the treasure tonight?"
    Marina "Но что если кто-нибудь другой найдет сегодня ночью сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s10a_2b30e12d:

    # "I don’t have an answer for that one."
    "No tengo respuesta para eso."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a716d1cd:

    # Amber "Guess we’ll just have to catch up then, huh?"
    Amber "Думаю, нам просто нужно их нагнать, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s10a_e33c31cc:

    # "Turning on the flashlight, I swing the beam around. While there’s still some daylight left, it isn’t much. Maybe half an hour at the most."
    "Al encender la linterna, barro el haz a mi alrededor. Aunque todavía queda algo de luz diurna, no es mucha. Tal vez media hora como máximo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:365
translate spanish hwb_s10a_60bc4dfd:

    # Marina "Catch up to what?"
    Marina "Нагнать что?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:367
translate spanish hwb_s10a_7776a50e:

    # Amber "The tour group, silly. Even if we’re late, they can’t have left that long ago. And they’ll be stopping a bunch so we should be able to find them easily."
    Amber "Экскурсионную группу, глупышка. Хотя мы и опоздали, они не могли уйти далеко. И они все равно будут останавливаться, поэтому по идее мы легко их отыщем."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s10a_55c8e499:

    # Marina "By ourselves?"
    Marina "Сами?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:371
translate spanish hwb_s10a_e35c92a7:

    # "Her voice is almost a squawk, like a surprised parrot."
    "Su voz es casi un graznido, como la de un loro sorprendido."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s10a_edfb993c:

    # Amber "Well, yeah. I don’t see anyone else around, do you?"
    Amber "Ну да, я что-то не вижу тут больше никого, а ты?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:379
translate spanish hwb_s10a_daf25f07:

    # "I swivel around, illuminating nothing but rocks and bushes."
    "Giro sobre mí mismo, iluminando solo rocas y arbustos."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s10a_8b5ede04:

    # Amber "C’mon, it’ll be fine. It’s not like there are gonna be bears or mountain lions this close to a parking lot."
    Amber "Да ладно тебе, все будет отлично. Тут же нет никаких медведей и горных львов так близко к парковке."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s10a_33833b6f:

    # Marina "Those kinds of things live here?!"
    Marina "Эти чудища здесь живут?!"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s10a_d2a2fe65:

    # "If she didn’t know that, then what is she afraid of?"
    "Si ella no sabía eso, ¿entonces de qué tiene miedo?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:387
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c3608974:

    # Amber "Probably. I don’t know. But come on, we’re wasting time."
    Amber "Возможно. Я не знаю. Пойдем уже, мы теряем время."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s10a_1cac1c76:

    # "Marina whimpers."
    "Marina gimotea."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s10a_6f2f3b7d:

    # "Then, surprising me, she grabs my hand. Hers is sweaty and warm."
    "Entonces, sorprendiéndome, agarra mi mano. La suya está sudada y caliente."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s10a_0414d908:

    # "I turn and look at her, and meet her wide eyes. It looks like she might cry, and makes me regret being so pushy."
    "Me giro y la miro, y me encuentro con sus ojos muy abiertos. Parece que podría llorar, y eso me hace arrepentirme de haber sido tan insistente."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s10a_d2c709ff:

    # Amber "We don’t have to do it if you don’t want to."
    Amber "Мы не обязаны это делать, если ты не хочешь."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s10a_2fa97240:

    # "She shakes her head, but clings to me like a kid, her free hand buried in my clothes. If it were any brighter out, she’d see my face turn red."
    "Ella niega con la cabeza, pero se aferra a mí como una niña, su mano libre hundida en mi ropa. Si hubiera más luz, vería mi cara enrojecerse."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s10a_81be9067:

    # Marina "No, like I said, if we don’t go now someone else will beat us to it."
    Marina "Нет, как я сказала, если мы не пойдем сейчас, то кто-нибудь нас опередит."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s10a_b1add55e:

    # Marina "Just… Stay close, okay?"
    Marina "Просто… Будь рядом, хорошо?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s10a_2175ced4:

    # Amber "Yeah, of course."
    Amber "Да, конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:418
translate spanish hwb_s10a_3c2a3c31:

    # "She lets me lead, but doesn’t let go of my hand. A large, wooden sign marks the start of the trail."
    "Ella me deja guiar, pero no suelta mi mano. Un gran cartel de madera marca el inicio del sendero."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s10a_4058bdd9:

    # Amber "So uh, are you scared of the dark?"
    Amber "Так ты, э-э, боишься темноты?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s10a_3512255f:

    # "No answer."
    "Sin respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s10a_cd8bd7ef:

    # Amber "But you were fine at Shiprock?"
    Amber "Но в Шипроке все было нормально?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s10a_3580c5f8:

    # Marina "That was different!"
    Marina "Там было по-другому!"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s10a_0a16ee03:

    # "Marina’s arm jerks, but she doesn’t let go."
    "El brazo de Marina da un tirón, pero no suelta."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s10a_42d2ec3b:

    # Marina "That was in a town."
    Marina "То было в городе."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s10a_edcf0919:

    # Marina "With people."
    Marina "С людьми."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s10a_52efed7d:

    # Marina "And roads."
    Marina "И дорогами."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s10a_79e7afb8:

    # Marina "And no mountain lions."
    Marina "И без горных львов."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s10a_4cf2150a:

    # "The temptation to tease her more is strong, but I don’t. Every time a bird caws or something makes the brush shake, I feel her flinch a little."
    "La tentación de molestarla más es fuerte, pero no lo hago. Cada vez que un pájaro grazna o algo hace crujir los arbustos, siento que ella se estremece un poco."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s10a_2f0a2568:

    # "Somehow, even this side of her is cute, too. A little childish, sure. But it's nice to have her rely on me to keep her safe."
    "De alguna manera, incluso este lado de ella también es lindo. Un poco infantil, claro. Pero es agradable que confíe en mí para mantenerla a salvo."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s10a_62ab0ee3:

    # "To take her mind off things, I make small talk."
    "Para distraerla, hago conversación trivial."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s10a_9f161249:

    # Amber "So, what are you gonna do once you’re filthy rich from the treasure?"
    Amber "Так, что ты собираешься делать, когда сокровище сделает тебя непристойно богатой?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s10a_80f271a1:

    # Marina "Sorry, what?"
    Marina "Прости, что?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s10a_706cfbbd:

    # Amber "I asked what you’ll do with your share of the treasure."
    Amber "Я спросила, что ты сделаешь со своей долей сокровища."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:472
translate spanish hwb_s10a_41034db3:

    # Marina "Oh, um… I’m not sure yet. I haven’t thought about it."
    Marina "О, эм… Я пока не уверена. Я об этом не думала."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:476
translate spanish hwb_s10a_5c73e79e:

    # Amber "We’re out here looking and you don’t even have a plan for it?"
    Amber "Мы ходим тут его разыскиваем, а ты даже не придумала, что будешь с ним делать?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c081338f:

    # Marina "It was a spur of the moment thing! What about you, huh?"
    Marina "Все это произошло слишком спонтанно! А что насчет тебя, м?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s10a_720d78bb:

    # Amber "I don’t know either."
    Amber "Я тоже не знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s10a_99dd2cdf:

    # Marina "Ha! See I’m not-"
    Marina "Ха! Видишь, я не одна-"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:492
translate spanish hwb_s10a_b286f978:

    # Amber "Yeah, yeah, but I wasn’t planning on looking for it, you know? I haven’t spent as much time thinking about it."
    Amber "Да, да, но я и не планировала искать его, понимаешь? Я не посвятила столько время раздумьям о нем."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:498
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a3ae8898:

    # "I glance behind me to see Marina stick out her tongue. I laugh."
    "Miro hacia atrás para ver a Marina sacar la lengua. Me río."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:502
translate spanish hwb_s10a_22251995:

    # Amber "But uh, let’s see. I definitely need to pay off Gramps' hospital and funeral expenses."
    Amber "Но, эм, давай подумаем. Мне точно нужно оплатить больничные счета дедушки и расходы на похороны."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s10a_8db9a01b:

    # Amber "After that, I guess I should probably get the motorhome fixed up. It’s not gonna break down on us or anything, but it’s kind of old."
    Amber "Потом, думаю, нужно бы починить трейлер. Вряд ли, конечно, что он сломается или типа того, но он довольно старый."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:518
translate spanish hwb_s10a_6843fe5d:

    # Marina "Why not just buy a new one?"
    Marina "Почему бы просто не купить новый?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:525
translate spanish hwb_s10a_55a8f675:

    # Amber "Hell no!"
    Amber "Что за бред!"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s10a_482b115c:

    # "My response comes out snappier than I intended."
    "Mi respuesta sale más cortante de lo que pretendía."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s10a_7560f758:

    # Amber "It’s just that it has sentimental value, you know? I’d rather keep that than buy a newer, better car."
    Amber "Просто он для меня много значит, понимаешь? Я лучше оставлю этот, чем куплю машину лучше и новее."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:533
translate spanish hwb_s10a_a5c809fe:

    # Amber "I grew up in that thing. I could never just replace it."
    Amber "Я выросла, катаясь в этом трейлере. Я бы никогда не смогла его заменить."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s10a_b888a263:

    # Amber "After that, I’d probably just keep doing what I was doing before I met you."
    Amber "Потом я, вероятно, продолжу заниматься тем, чем занималась до встречи с тобой."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:539
translate spanish hwb_s10a_8bcb6c31:

    # Marina "And what's that?"
    Marina "И чем это?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:543
translate spanish hwb_s10a_475704e5:

    # Amber "Wandering."
    Amber "Странствовать."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:547
translate spanish hwb_s10a_452a6382:

    # Marina "Don’t you wanna stop wandering sometime?"
    Marina "Ты не хочешь когда-нибудь прекратить свои странствия?"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s10a_d233d2aa:

    # "My steps slow a bit. It’s an innocent question, but it hits me hard."
    "Mis pasos se ralentizan un poco. Es una pregunta inocente, pero me golpea fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:551
translate spanish hwb_s10a_5492aeb4:

    # Amber "Not yet, no."
    Amber "Пока нет, нет."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:553
translate spanish hwb_s10a_e80e0f9f:

    # "I whisper it."
    "Lo susurro."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:555
translate spanish hwb_s10a_8ee4c69e:

    # "Marina catches up next to me, dropping my hand as she does so."
    "Marina se pone a mi lado, soltando mi mano mientras lo hace."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s10a_93e82016:

    # Marina "Pfft, at least I’m not the only one without a goal."
    Marina "Пфф, по крайней мере, я не одна, у кого нет цели."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:563
translate spanish hwb_s10a_1e40c6ff:

    # "I poke her in the side and she squirms away a couple feet."
    "Le doy un codazo en el costado y ella se aleja unos pasos retorciéndose."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:568
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c5b9c6dd:

    # Marina "Ow!"
    Marina "Ой!"

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:570
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c8ff6963:

    # Amber "Dork."
    Amber "Дурачина."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s10a_c2c846ef:

    # "It’s hard to stay sad around her."
    "Es difícil estar triste a su lado."

# game/script/hwb_s10a.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s10a_6c00923c:

    # "I laugh, causing her to turn away smiling. She’s a lot cuter when she smiles."
    "Me río, haciendo que ella se dé la vuelta sonriendo. Es mucho más linda cuando sonríe."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s10a.rpy:601
    old "Catching up to the tour group"
    new "Catching up to the tour group"

